channel.title: An Empty World [Automatic Regeneration...]
channel.description:
~~Hmm... I know people want to roleplay and all...~~
~~But the world is empty.~~ ~~You cant do anything if there's nothing in the place to actually talk about, right?~~
~~So let's introduce something!~~
~~And... hey, while you guys can introduce characters, worlds and all... make sure that they aren't dimensions apart. I'll have to work to link them together!~~
~~Don't be too hard on me, okay?~~
------------------------
So... I have many ideas. But I know you have more.
This is your world. Build upon it. Break logic... or adhere to it. Go forth and bloom...
My beauti-.
W-what is that? That looks disgusting! What even is that? There's Americans fighting Canadians in one corner, and a magical bus filled with a hundred people, keeping them like guinea pigs... and they're being invaded... and minecrafters... on a single diamond oh my-
And there are... fortniters... and wh-
No no no! It's all wrong! ![artworks-000409329321-k0o0os-t500x500|500x500, 50%](upload://CEv8MH5CwX4LZ8hpFYeAw7ed4w.jpeg)
------------------
``` The world has been destroyed. Creating new empty world.
Dedicated Deity: Shurian.
Created World Files. Created People Files. Created Relationship Files. Created Magic Files.
...
Filling New World. ```
_Well... let's just say I'm saving everyone from a deformed gremlin of a world..._
Besides, that teardrop planet doesn't sound too bad. Thank you @GGhana.
"Well... There's the wor- Oh, you can't see the world? Oh, I swore I changed the privacy settings on this... Tell you what, you can always check back later! Technology doesn't like me one bit..."

item.description:
Subject Alpha walks to her quarantine in a sealed corridor at the back of the laboratory where the conversation was just had. When she arrives she falls onto her bed and falls unconcious.

She feels somehow, not real. Like she was just abducted by aliens. She feels like a puppet for a couple of unknown others. Will this be the worst mistake she ever made in her life? Only time will tell, for now it is time for sleep

item.title: An Empty World [Automatic Regeneration...]
item.dc:creator: GGhana
item.description:
CUT AWAY

NEW SCENE

a woman in a labcoat speaks to a woman in casual clothes, almost looking like pajamas

The woman in a labcoat says “Subject Alpha, I think we can both agree that this was a great test. I appreciate your sacrifice, our experiments with prisoners were never as successful as this. It is clear that we needed someone with an indepth knowledge of the system. Anyways enough with the flattery. The real congratulations is the fact we have managed to bring something from the timestream into the physical world. We’re not entirely sure what adverse consequences there might be from this but at this point I think we can both agree that this is huge.”

The other woman just nods her head.

The woman in the labcoat says “Unfortunately you have to take a month long quarantine to make sure any adverse effects wear off. But we will try to make it as pleasent as possible. Thank you and have a good day.”

The other woman walks off.
